sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Edge Device
    participant E as Edge Management System
    participant O as System Operator
    participant A as Application Publisher
    participant C as Optional Application Certifier

    Note over O,E: Operator approval and deployment preparation
    O->>E: Import publisher certificate
    O->>E: Import application image
    O->>E: Import certification record
    E->>E: Verify publisher signature
    E->>E: Verify certification record
    E->>E: Apply operator policy
    E->>E: Create deployment manifest
    E->>E: Sign deployment manifest

    O->>E: Deploy application and manifest
    E->>D: Transfer application and manifest
    D->>D: Verify application image hash
    D->>D: Verify operator authorization
    D->>D: Verify local trust requirements
    D->>D: Install application

    Note over O,D: Application activation
    O->>E: Activate application
    E->>D: Activate application
    D->>D: Launch application
    D->>D: Record application logs
    D-->>E: Report application status
